{"tid":2081081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理買野定行街，七一見","createTime":"2020-06-27T02:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:04:27.000Z","uid":38177,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"df18e1891a435616edf3f896ad065ad7f6d2cd20","tid":2081081,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNBikyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNBikyt.png&h=ab586844&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzUS9rQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzUS9rQ.png&h=2a61540f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfeDkyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfeDkyy.jpg&h=fcfd839b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RY8gRFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRY8gRFi.png&h=d45eda46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原諒我偷圖⋯⋯"},{"pid":"46b8f44966a56ca9e37be53d2f0177219660f2f0","tid":2081081,"uid":184216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"258e7df8eb872f4c63189aa52a1e93de843276b6","tid":2081081,"uid":38177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"我老豆都話出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前佢都未出過"},{"pid":"8fbfc302d88125987a66579ae4079b31fb48d425","tid":2081081,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">李柱銘不代表我，我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9a7941c142942e8532374d2f18a99249c926ac70","tid":2081081,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d26edafee0e8e0ba27533ba7f836ce21739a7d","tid":2081081,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"出呀七一"},{"pid":"2e30d0df1d8c1a99ea3b7a6a159a0a92cfa132d5","tid":2081081,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"七一見"},{"pid":"9aa416b60cf7dbe909cdea495af5805af1f27f98","tid":2081081,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ce503e46107f88079ffa7da89465fb162575ad2","tid":2081081,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c866e4c2bc2ecb41ddc92f08382d4008297a2c","tid":2081081,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"七一唔出嚟反對國安法 英國到時話香港市民話樂見國安法 BNO冇必要擴權 <br />\n為公為私 七一 上街"},{"pid":"942bd4